According to Reuters, records presented at the hearing showed that in a group Signal chat with other agents, Exum wrote: “I fired 5 rounds and she had 7 holes. I wired both the pendant lamp and the standing lamp myself, and added dimmable LED bulbs with heart-shaped filaments.
